reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 7, 2020
reviews.reviewText: This is an amazing product. We were on a trip, and the sinus ache I had was getting worse. I flossed every day and still had an ache and unexplainable discomfort in my gums. (Yes, I go to the dentist regularly). With a week ahead of us, away from home, I came across this wash in a Whole Foods in Richmond, VA. A few swishes of this (very strong tasting and smelling— in a good way) wash and my ache subsided. I used it for the remainder of the week away and had NO discomfort from, what turned out to be a need to have a root canal. A rotten freakin’ root, that caused discomfort and a weird smell that- the OLD dentist missed for maybe 2 years- No joke, this wash works.New dentist is great and a 4 hour procedure gave me a lovely porcelain crown.In addition, my husband had an itchy “roof of mouth” thing going on and within 2 swishes, it was gone. Maybe it was allergies... we don’t know.It feels good, it smells good.. it’s REALLY strong. I recommend this if you’re having a weird mouth thing.

reviews.reviewText: This is a great product for a fair value. The fact it has no alcohol/fluoride sold me (they put fluoride in everything these days including water!)
